{"tid":218555,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"撤下簡體中文標語　韓國樂天改攻港、日、台遊客","createTime":"2017-04-26T15:04:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T15:56:23.000Z","uid":62257,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"226bf300478fba081bbb09d20f822dfed242fed1","tid":218555,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:04:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170426/1105747\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20170426%2F1105747&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXOI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=db55dbc8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170426/1105747</a><br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170426/640_438c5522f6d4c8dcf637853964bb2f1f.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170426%2F640_438c5522f6d4c8dcf637853964bb2f1f.jpg&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXOI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=a9f1966f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170426/640_438c5522f6d4c8dcf637853964bb2f1f.jpg</a><br />\n[/img]2017年04月26日12:46      <br />\n南韓樂天集團因和南韓軍方換地、部署薩德飛彈防禦系統而遭中國遊客抵制。根據南韓媒體報導，樂天從原本企圖挽回陸客的做法改為吸引日、港、台及東南亞旅客，原本專為陸客設置的中文標語也默默撤下。<br />\n《亞洲經濟》今日報導，位於首爾中區的樂天百貨總店，一個月前還四處可見寫著「因為理解，所以等待」的中文標語，但如今卻只看見寫著日文及英文的折扣促銷廣告。樂天百貨相關人士對此表示：「我們正在改變以吸引中國遊客為主的政策。」<br />\n報導指出，樂天和香港、台灣及新加坡等10間旅行社簽訂合作契約，只要遊客透過這些旅行社訪韓，便可獲贈購物預付卡。此外，自4月28日至5月7日，外國遊客持明洞商圈的購物發票可換取1萬韓元金額的樂天百貨店專用預付卡兌換券。樂天百貨店行銷部門負責人金大洙（音譯）說：「我們正在進行多種宣傳，來吸引日本、東南亞及中東等世界各國家和地區的遊客。」<br />\n由於中國遊客銳減，樂天百貨店總店的銷售額減少了20-30%。陸客一度占樂天百貨店外國人整體消費額的88%，但今年3月已降至72%。而日本遊客的消費比重則從去年的2.3%增至今年3月的11.6%。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170426/420_693e1eb35722fa1e282c5de4c776fc77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170426%2F420_693e1eb35722fa1e282c5de4c776fc77.jpg&h=47671588&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樂天集團逐漸撤下向陸客喊話的簡體中文標語。"},{"pid":"2746a9c646d6262a26f83f569a3d5bd288b1ef02","tid":218555,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170426/640_438c5522f6d4c8dcf637853964bb2f1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170426%2F640_438c5522f6d4c8dcf637853964bb2f1f.jpg&h=e7dc15a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e44d4a163ac62f0d11bee8403735fb25c8fce349","tid":218555,"uid":28515,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:07:09.000Z","msg":"關我撚事<br />\n韓國點樣都唔去啦"},{"pid":"3e1ebd07c34b75d52cca673b8dee78d43a54f21e","tid":218555,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:08:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170426/640_438c5522f6d4c8dcf637853964bb2f1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170426%2F640_438c5522f6d4c8dcf637853964bb2f1f.jpg&h=e7dc15a8&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n當堂高質晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f57dd777cf80932b301c14647ce2d833024219","tid":218555,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f45f2f62a58fcd66e7ac1355f02a77df7c0274e","tid":218555,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:46:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94629fc45416149699993b11f393ccff529d6963","tid":218555,"uid":72186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:54:06.000Z","msg":"雖然唔會去但樂見有更多國家抵制陸客"},{"pid":"5227fc80c600e7013bd197d48a733fa344fba5a4","tid":218555,"uid":331